      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/File:Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4d/Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg/250px-Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"267\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4d/Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg/330px-Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4d/Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg/500px-Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Maurits_Cornelis_Escher.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Maurits (M.C.) Escher, around Nov. 23, 1971</div></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M._C._Escher\">Maurits Cornelis Escher</a>, (June 17, 1898 – March 27, 1972)<br />\nwas a Dutch graphic artist who made <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematics_and_art\">mathematically-inspired</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woodcut\">woodcuts</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lithography\">lithographs</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mezzotint\">mezzotints</a>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Links\">Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:M._C._Escher&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mcescher.com/\">M.C. Escher - The Official Website</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mcescher.com/gallery/\">M.C. Escher – Gallery</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Maurits_Cornelis_Escher\">Category:Maurits Cornelis Escher - Wikimedia Commons</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://escherdroste.math.leidenuniv.nl/\">Escher and the Droste effect</a> - <a href=\"/Leiden_University\" title=\"Leiden University\">Universiteit Leiden</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Recursion\" title=\"Recursion\">Recursion</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:Kraan\" title=\"Category:Kraan\">Kraan</a> -  M.C. Escher (1972), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/AAm1kwx4nnE?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:M._C._Escher&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mcescher.com/licensing/\">All works by M.C. Escher are copyrighted</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301105655\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.088 seconds\nReal time usage: